data.description: Welcome home to this BEAUTIFUL three-bedroom, two-bath brick home. 4 Bobby Jones is located on the golf course home in a beautiful setting with a beautiful view on Hilltop's #8 Fairway. Master bedroom is located away from the other two bedrooms.  Living Room is complete with a beautiful brick fireplace and an incredible view of the back yard and the golf course. Your minutes from the Pro Shop and all the amenities Hilltop has to offer. Enjoy the spacious patio overlooking the #8 fairway, often with more deer playing on it than golfers. Hilltop Lakes is a POA (Property Owner’s Assn) & amenities include a challenging and fun 18-Hole Golf Course, five lakes, equestrian facilities (see stall rates), 3,000’ paved, lighted airport runway, Texas-shaped, Texas-sized swimming pool, tennis courts, putt-putt golf course, fire deptartment, bow-hunting club, lots of friendly neighbors & so much more! Located in the heart of the Texas Triangle, Hilltop Lakes is almost equi-distance from Houston, Dallas & San Antonio and only roughly 45 minutes from Texas A & M and your favorite SEC sports. Call us today for your showing.
